.SS "Application Options:"
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Generate machine\-readable output
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Show version numbers
.PP
Queries font file for various information. If no query option is specified, \fB\-\-show\-all\fR is assumed.
